That's because we think that the Cyber Resilience Act is one of the most pivotal legislation

59:35.240 --> 59:36.640
that we are going to have.

59:36.640 --> 59:40.120
Well, now we're this funded, but in general, it's a trendsetter.

59:40.120 --> 59:42.320
It's a very, very important legislation.

59:42.320 --> 59:48.920
At Digital Europe, we do sort of internal search to see what is important for our members

59:48.920 --> 59:56.240
