01:30:05.080 --> 01:30:09.800
On this concept of commercial, so first, I mean, I think it would be very difficult for

01:30:09.800 --> 01:30:14.360
us to replace it by another concept because it's well grounded in this new legislative

01:30:14.360 --> 01:30:15.920
framework.

01:30:15.920 --> 01:30:21.280
