But we're absolutely prepared to provide examples once it has come into force so that you have

01:34:15.320 --> 01:34:19.680
the certainty that you need to know whether you are in the scope or not with your project.

01:34:19.680 --> 01:34:22.280
I think I took them all.

01:34:22.280 --> 01:34:26.880
I think, yeah, of course.

