01:35:07.120 --> 01:35:13.280
So we always tried, obviously, to reach as much as possible.

01:35:13.280 --> 01:35:15.840
The thing is, obviously, there are sometimes channels.

01:35:15.840 --> 01:35:20.880
It's not that we avoid having talks with the people that can criticise the legislation.

01:35:20.880 --> 01:35:23.560
We need critics to also make the legislation better.

01:35:23.560 --> 01:35:25.640
This is how it works.

01:35:25.640 --> 01:35:33.080
So obviously, as you said, that, yeah, there might be some players that are more voiceable.

01:35:33.080 --> 01:35:35.360
This is the reality.

01:35:35.360 --> 01:35:41.560
