So I understand that there is this need of clarification.

01:36:51.640 --> 01:36:56.240
This is where the definitions are there.

01:36:56.240 --> 01:37:01.800
But they are also the basics of any legislation that we have in the union.

01:37:01.800 --> 01:37:10.040
It's not that simple to change just one definition that is common to all of them in one single

01:37:10.040 --> 01:37:11.040
piece of legislation.

01:37:11.040 --> 01:37:15.920
This is also the reality of how the proposal works.

01:37:15.920 --> 01:37:17.800
You need coherence.

01:37:17.800 --> 01:37:20.200
You can have some exclusions.

